  "description": "<h4>1. JOB DESCRIPTION</h4>\n<p>Job Title</p>\n<p>Admin &amp; Account assistant</p>\n<p>Occupation</p>\n<p>Administration Clerk</p>\n<h5>Job Description &amp; Requirements</h5>\n<p>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</p>\n<p>Administrative</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide administrative and operational support</li>\n  <li>Purchasing of supplies, materials, equipment, renewal of certificates and licensing etc</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with vendors and follow up on service contracts</li>\n  <li>Ensure business processes and documentations etc are in compliance with Government standards and regulations</li>\n  <li>Issuance / arrangement of sales and purchase related documents and transactions</li>\n  <li>Any other duties assigned</li>\n  <li>Able to read and write in English, Chinese / Mandarin</li>\n  <li>Proficient in Microsoft Office programs</li>\n  <li>Initiative and requires minimum supervision at work</li>\n  <li>Good attitude and willing to learn</li>\n  <li>Minimum ITE or Diploma qualification</li>\n  <li>Work experience in office administration will be an advantage</li>\n  <li>Skill &amp; knowledge on Sage will be an advantage</li>\n  <li>3~5 years expenerice</li>\n  <li>Singaporeans &amp; PRs may apply</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Benefits</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Same as full time employee</li>\n  <li>Medical reimbursement</li>\n  <li>Transport allowance</li>\n</ul>",
